Interface EmployeeRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee,Integer>, GenericRepository<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee,Integer>
@Repository @Transactional(readOnly=true) public interface EmployeeRepository extends GenericRepository<com.enttribe.hrms.model.Employee>
The EmployeeRepository interface is a extension of GenericRepository. It's purpose is to provide additional methods that are specific to the Employee entity. see GenericRepository see JpaRepository
